"""
Parameter Sweep — Rolling Window / Threshold / Stop Loss
=========================================================
Entry/exit based on:
  1. Price vs message DENSITY correlation >= threshold
  2. Normalised sentiment > 0 (net bullish) to enter
     Sentiment turns negative to exit

Per-cap fixed windows (when not sweeping window):
  nano  :  80 min
  micro :  40 min
  small :  60 min
  mid   : 350 min
  large :  90 min
  mega  :  60 min

Sweeps:
  threshold    : 0.1 → 1.0  (step 0.1)
  rolling window: 10 → 960  (step 10)
  stop loss    : 10, 20, 30 ... 100%

Requirements:
    pip install curl_cffi pandas scipy pytz
"""

